|    1 | 自定义变量      | 356a192b7913b04c54574d18c28d46e6395428ab | da4b9237bacccdf19c0760cab7aec4a8359010b0 | 4e07408562bedb8b60ce05c1decfe3ad16b72230967de01f640b7e4729b49fce |
|    2 | 全局变量        | 356a192b7913b04c54574d18c28d46e6395428ab | da4b9237bacccdf19c0760cab7aec4a8359010b0 | 4e07408562bedb8b60ce05c1decfe3ad16b72230967de01f640b7e4729b49fce |
|    3 | 参数变量        | 356a192b7913b04c54574d18c28d46e6395428ab | da4b9237bacccdf19c0760cab7aec4a8359010b0 | 4e07408562bedb8b60ce05c1decfe3ad16b72230967de01f640b7e4729b49fce |
